{title: SVG Section}

{start_of_verse}
[C]Vector graphics [G]in the song
[Am]Scalable and [F]crisp
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_svg}
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="200" height="100" viewBox="0 0 200 100">
  <rect x="10" y="10" width="180" height="80" fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"/>
  <text x="100" y="55" text-anchor="middle" font-family="serif" font-size="16">
    Inline SVG
  </text>
  <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="10" fill="blue"/>
  <circle cx="170" cy="30" r="10" fill="red"/>
</svg>
{end_of_svg}

{start_of_chorus}
[F]Pictures drawn in [C]code
[G]Embedded in the [Am]song
[F]Scalable to [C]any size
[G]Always sharp and [C]strong
{end_of_chorus}
